1118
01:13:13,589 --> 01:13:15,955
I'm not Francis.

1119
01:13:16,024 --> 01:13:18,686
I'm not lying to you.
I'm not cheating on you.

1120
01:13:18,761 --> 01:13:20,626
- I'm definitelynot avoiding you.
