about my part in this.

1153
01:15:50,178 --> 01:15:52,806
I think you did
the right thing, Lisa.

1154
01:15:53,348 --> 01:15:55,213
You know,
even love won't guarantee...

1155
01:15:55,284 --> 01:15:57,479
